  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Eiger Mountain and Soul Resort is offered on a bed and breakfast board basis and the hotel restaurant provides an excellent hot and cold buffet breakfast each morning.</p>
<p>There is free daily tea, coffee and cake between 3-5pm).</p>
<p>Each room has a free minibar with soft drinks, beer and mineral water, replenished daily.</p>
<p>Evening meals are available in the hotel restaurant or, alternatively, there are great local restaurants within a few minutes walk</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Formerly know as the Eiger Hotel, the <span>Eiger Mountain &amp; Soul Resort is a</span> super family-run hotel right in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6cb1f0178b7447488bbf36b5f109fbc}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald.</a> It is a particular favourite in our programme for its excellent standards of accommodation and cuisine, its welcoming atmosphere and its convenient location.</p>
<h2>Working with nature</h2>
<p><span>Take your time, enjoy the moment and recharge your batteries in nature. Tucked right into the stunning mountain scenery, the Eiger Mountain &amp; Soul Resort is a total recharge zone. It's all about that good mountain vibe, mixed with some</span><span> comfy living that provides you with a real connection to nature. The rooms are all furnished with natural materials such as stone and wood and decorated in natural tones so you can really appreciate the surrounding views.</span></p>
<h2><span>Spa and wellness facilities</span></h2>
<p><span>The Eiger Mountain and Soul Resort provides a range of wellness facilities for you to use during your stay. You will find a fitness area with a supervised workout programme, a variety of massages and beauty treatments and a SPA with saunas, private whirlpool and kneipp pool. If you'd prefer a more personal approach to your relaxation, a private spa is available for exclusive moments at a local charge.</span></p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
