  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>A lovely family-run hotel right in the centre of Grindelwald, the Eiger Mountain and Soul Resort available on a bed and breakfast basis, is a particular favourite in our programme for its excellent standards of accommodation and cuisine as well as its friendly welcome, range of spa facilities and efforts to connect with nature.</p>]]></listingDescription>
