  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is centrally located on the resort's main street and is approx. six minutes' walk (400 metres) to the gondola for 'First' ski area.</p>
<p>It is a seven minutes' walk (700 metres) to the station for the mountain train to Kleine Scheidegg for access to Wengen.</p>
<p>There is a ski bus stop for both just a couple of minutes' walk from hotel.</p>]]></locationDescription>
