  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Lifestyle Chic</strong> <strong>Austrian Twin Rooms</strong> are around 22<span>m²</span> and sleep up to four guests with bunk beds (max 3 adults or 2 adults and 2 children under 12). All rooms have a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Lifestyle View</strong> <strong>Rooms</strong> have king or twin beds, and are around 22-25<span>m². These rooms </span>face the road side and have a balcony and Eiger views.</p>
<p><strong>Lifestyle Comfort Austrian Twin Rooms</strong> are around 21-25m<span>²</span> and are generally quieter rooms. They have a balcony and lovely south-facing views</p>
<p><strong>Lifestyle Single</strong> <strong>Rooms</strong> are around 22m<span>²</span> and are west-facing and have a balcony or terrace.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities: </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cable/satellite TV</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Hairdryer </li>
<li>Mini bar</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
